  "content_html": "<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:16px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"text-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 4px 5px;\"><a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" href=\"https://www.elnet-meter.com\" target=\"_self\"><span class=\"color_11 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Control Applications</span></span></span></a></span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h2 class=\"font_2 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:70px; line-height:0.9em;\"><span class=\"color_30 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.05em;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:70px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:helvetica-w01-bold,helvetica-w02-bold,helvetica-lt-w10-bold,sans-serif;\">About us</span></span></span></span></span></h2></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\">Control Applications Ltd.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"letter-spacing:normal;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">Control Applications (CA) is a private company that manufacture computerized control systems PLC/DDC &amp; controllers, Building Automation systems (BMS), Electrical Power meters and Analysers, Power factor correction controllers, Automatic Transfer Switches (ATS) and more…</p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">CA’s measurements and control systems consist of both hardware and software products that are user-friendly as well as being technically superior.</p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">The products that stands at the centre or CA’s activities intended to measure monitor and control electrical networks' air conditioning systems as well as all the electromechanical systems that installed in public building.</p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">The products intended for use in the industry, public buildings, hotels, hospitals, universities, shopping centres and more.  .</p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\">Control Applications Ltd. is the leading company in Israel. The high quality and efficiency of CA’s products recognized by their long list of satisfied customers all over the world.</p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\">CA’s measurements and control systems consist of both hardware and software products that are user-friendly as well as being technically superior. the products that stands at the center or CA’s activities is intended to measure ,monitor and control electrical networks as well as electromechanical systems. The products are intended for use in industry, public buildings, hotels, hospitals, universities, shopping centers and more.  .</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text\">​</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\">Control Applications Ltd. is the leading company in Israel. The high quality and efficiency of CA’s products are recognized by their long list of satisfied customers all over the world .</span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:helvetica-w01-light,helvetica-w02-light,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Quality Assurance</span></span></span></span></h3>\n<h3 class=\"font_3 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><br class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"/>\n<span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:helvetica-w01-light,helvetica-w02-light,sans-serif;\">We are committed to our goal to provide products of exceptional quality and the most efficient service. The Standards Institute of Israel, ISO 9001 and ISO 9000.3 recognize that Control Applications maintains a high level of quality in all areas of their activities including development, production, supplying and installation of the systems. In addition, the company’s equipment conforms to CE Directives and Standards.</span></span></span></h3></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:22px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Control Applications</span></span></span></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Contact Us</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Phone: +972-3-6474998</span><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">​</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Fax: +972-3-6474598</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:left;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Email: <a class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" data-auto-recognition=\"true\" href=\"mailto:cal@ddc.co.il\">cal@ddc.co.il</a></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Opening Hour</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">Control Applications</span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Sun - Thu</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;\">08:00 - 17:00</span></p></div>\n<div class=\"rich-text\"><p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px; text-align:right;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:arial,ｍｓ ｐゴシック,ms pgothic,돋움,dotum,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Adress</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"font_7 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size: